000100************************************************************              
000200* CERD022                                                  *              
000300************************************************************              
000400*    RECORD PURPOSE: INVENTORY BALANCE UPLOAD              *              
000500*        FROM RDM (UNIX) TO HOST (IBM)                     *              
000600*    RECORD LENGTH:  128 BYTES                             *              
000700*    RECORD FORMAT:  SEQUENTIAL                            *              
000710*                                                          *              
000720*    OF NOTE:  WHEN BEING LOADED FROM CES, THE             *              
000721*    ALLOCATABLE UNITS ARE BEING MOVED TO THE CE022-       *              
000722*    AVAIL-UNITS FIELD AND THE UNALLOCATABLE UNITS ARE     *              
000723*    BEING MOVED TO THE CE022-DISTRIB-UNITS FIELD.         *              
000800************************************************************              
